OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with largely clear skies,
OL,7,Falthough a veil of high cloud will
OL,8,Fmove over at times. A patchy rural
OL,9,Ffrost is possible in the coldest
OL,10,Fspots. Staying gusty over the hills.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,13,Facross the region. After a chilly
OL,14,Fstart, it will warm up through the
OL,15,Fday, although a brisk wind will make
OL,16,Fit feel fresh in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
